    "headline": "Broadridge Announces Pricing of $500,000,000 Senior Notes",
    "summary": "Broadridge Financial Solutions, Inc. (NYSE:BR) (\"Broadridge\") today announced that it has priced $500,000,000 aggregate principal amount of 5.750% senior notes due 2036 (the \"Notes\") in an offering registered under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended. Broadridge intends to use the net proceeds of this offering, together with cash on hand, to repay its outstanding 3.400% senior notes due 2026.",
